# Product Schema

## Core Product Models

The product system consists of several related models:

- @Product - The main product model
  - Has attributes like Title, Description, CoverImage, Media, Status
  - Related to categories, variations, reviews, tags, FAQs
  
- @Product Variation - Represents different variants of a product
  - Connected to product variation colors and sizes
  - Contains pricing, stock, and SKU information
  
- @Product Variation Model - Model templates for product variations
  
## Product Categorization
  
- @Product Category - Hierarchical categories for products
  - Can be main category or additional categories for products
  - Contains fields like Name, Image, ParentCategory
  
- @Product Category Content - Content for product categories

- @Product Tag - Tags for product filtering and organization

## Product Variants

- @Product Variation Color - Color options for product variations
- @Product Variation Size - Size options for product variations
- @Product Size Helper - Size guide for products

## Product Feedback

- @Product Review - Customer reviews for products
- @Product Review Reply - Replies to product reviews
- @Product Review Like - Likes on product reviews
- @Product Like - User likes for products
- @Product FAQ - Frequently asked questions about products

## Product Inventory

- @Product Stock - Stock management for products
- @Product Stock Log - Logs of stock changes

